##check container limits 
$docker stats 


#to check swap memory is enabled or not
$docker info --> if no swap limit warning then we have to edit the grub file, check following link for better understandment

https://docs.docker.com/engine/install/linux-postinstall/#your-kernel-does-not-support-cgroup-swap-limit-capabilities 


